data.description: Welcome to this charming 3BR 2BA rambler situated in a highly sought-after neighborhood. With over 1100 sq ft of living space, this home offers a cozy and comfortable atmosphere. As you enter you will immediately notice the inviting layout and warm ambiance. The open  concept design seamlessly connects the living room, dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for family gatherings or just entertaining friends. This home also boasts a 2 car attached garage, offering secure parking and extra storage for your vehicles and belongings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful rambler your new home, contact your favorite Realtor to schedule a showing today.
